<p><strong>内容</strong>：史异，人变，归常<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-5" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-5')">5</a></sup>。</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>回信</strong>：████</p>
